body:
@bessbd I'll have a look at this later today and we can talk through together what's up.

If you try to follow the steps in https://github.com/apache/couchdb/blob/main/build-aux/Jenkinsfile.full (this is run after any merge to `main`) by hand, using the Docker images, can you reproduce it?

It may be as simple as re-building the Docker containers and re-pushing them. This is not currently done automatically.
